In large mixing bowl, combine KELLOGG'S(R) CRISPIX(R) cereal and pecans. Set aside. In small bowl, stir together remaining ingredients. Pour over cereal mixture, tossing until evenly coated. Place on 15 x 10 x 1-inch jellyroll pan coated with cooking spray. Bake at 300 degrees F about 30 minutes stirring twice. Cool completely. Store in airtight container.